    • search

      public boolean search​(int k, int timeAllowed, long timeStart, boolean boxes)
      recusive method that seafches for the best score for a set amount of time
      Parameters:
      k - : indicator of what layer we are on, starts at 0, incremented each recursion
      timeAllowed - : time in ms given for it to run
      timeStart - : the time the algorithm is started
      boxes - : boolean that determines wether we are using boxes, or pentominoes
      Returns:
      boolean that specifies if a solution (complete cover) has been found
